des: "This tastes just like a real chocolate ice cream shake and can be made soy and dairy free! Substitute almond butter or cashew butter for peanut butter; omit agave syrup if banana is extremely ripe."
ins: Blend coconut milk, banana, cocoa powder, peanut butter, agave syrup, and ice cubes in a blender until smooth and slushy; pour into glasses and serve.
